task.summary: - Fixed game loop. - Changed frame buffer to 2 instead of 3. - Added GScreen to ease screen rendering. - Added GEntity as base class for future entities. - Added GEntity list to keep track of entities. - Added GRenderable interface for all renderable objects.
- Entities can now move. - tickDeltaTime is corrected to microseconds due to imprecision in double. - Graphics refresh each frame.

- Entities can now rotate, although errors persist. - Pixels now have their own class. - Custom frame GFrame class, includes bottom textField. - Positions are now stored in custom GVector2 class. - Entity class updated to store positions in double rather than int. - Started GCommander class to handle input.
- Added locations - Added Items - Added Player - Refined GCommander to parse commands and call action on items
- Added location derived classes - Locations are managed by connections - Locations now self initialize - Items now respond correctly to commands - Added support for "with" command - Fixed small bugs
- Added the whole conversation with Bartender of Nassau Pub, which: - Started the quest regarding the missing schedule - Introduced Captain Hume - Fixed typos and stuff
- Added the sea pun conversation line to the Bartender conversation
- Added the conversation with The Punmaster of Nassau
